174 A.3d 507 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. PABLO ANTONIO ACEVEDO, A/K/A ERIC RUIZ, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-197 September Term 2017

079458 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000304-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
